{"tid":666751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"幻視呢個角色真係香港人嘅代表","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T08:44:53.000Z","uid":185935,"like":83,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"666cd8c77a3b3d4b8d041a7ce21e6e26b7f47647","tid":666751,"uid":185935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"本來有個老竇<br />\n之後升呢多咗個身份，勁咗好撚多<br />\n<br />\n本來可以獨立，但次次都舔老竇鞋底助紂為虐，話就話講法律，其實係誅除異己。<br />\n<br />\n著衫跟風，見雷神有斗篷佢又要有，喂，神域fashion關你叉事？<br />\n<br />\n你屌佢咩，佢冇所謂，因為已經溝咗件大波妹，有奶便是贏。<br />\n<br />\n到咗真係出事有危險，佢選舉叫條女幫手，將自己嘅未來交畀人地去決定。<br />\n<br />\n佢滿口理論又點，大家都有眼睇，最後喺滅霸手上，佢係0反抗。<br />\n<br />\n比著你揀你做唔做幻視？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做，有大波波就ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔做，香港人要命運自決"},{"pid":"d33e78992568cb87dea9ac56aa0d0647e7c5115e","tid":666751,"uid":63588,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"投你老母"},{"pid":"8fe36e9b2855a1f3886e754224532eb6ff9ef19c","tid":666751,"uid":176368,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"on9 1999"},{"pid":"34f732dcd304b8a0e8c02f9fc3717e6d4231558d","tid":666751,"uid":65780,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384e08ca74a0797317e3fb8a26acc52780032e5e","tid":666751,"uid":12471,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"你噏乜鳩呀"},{"pid":"43f7cd294f1ddce4e35c012c672acea9aecad400","tid":666751,"uid":54927,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"睇唔撚明樓主想講乜"},{"pid":"08820a87419ab9fa16378ad5fa63e3a0f5f8da8b","tid":666751,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"850a1fc2d2a27d11443cf9931dccd8